OL,3,CNew native woodland set to be created
OL,4,Cin Scottish Borders
OL,6,FA new native woodland is set to be
OL,7,Fcreated in the Scottish Borders with
OL,8,F45 hectares near Tweedsmuir due to be
OL,9,Ftransformed.
OL,11,FThe Scottish Water scheme around the
OL,12,FTalla Reservoir is aimed at making the
OL,13,Farea more resilient to climate change
OL,14,Fand improving biodiversity.
