OL,3,CNew native woodland set to be created
OL,4,Cin Scottish Borders
OL,6,FElise Cartmell from Scottish Water,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are going to be planting
OL,8,Ftrees here using a mixture of hand
OL,9,Fplanting but then also for the first
OL,10,Ftime we are going to be using a drone
OL,11,Fto help seed the more inaccessible and
OL,12,Fhigher areas.
OL,14,F"What we are hoping is that in time
OL,15,Fthe soil with the tree roots will be
OL,16,Fable to retain more of that rain,
OL,17,Fespecially during intense rainfall
OL,18,Fperiods. It will then be able to
OL,19,Frecharge the area so that under
OL,20,Fdrought conditions more of that can be
OL,21,Freleased."
