OL,3,CNew native woodland set to be created
OL,4,Cin Scottish Borders
OL,6,FThe project is set to fully get
OL,7,Funderway at the end of this year but
OL,8,Fsome saplings have already been
OL,9,Fplanted.
OL,11,FSam Guthrie, forest manager said: "We
OL,12,Fplanted trees in January at the
OL,13,Fbeginning of the year and they are
OL,14,Fcoming along quite well at the minute.
