OL,3,CNew native woodland set to be created
OL,4,Cin Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"There are deer present on the site
OL,7,Fand we employ a local stalker to look
OL,8,Fafter deer management, to protect the
OL,9,Ftrees. There is a lot that goes into
OL,10,Fthe plan and design of a woodland like
OL,11,Fthis, we do soil assessment and we
OL,12,Falso employ professional ecologists."
OL,14,FDuring hot days in the summer months
OL,15,Fthe trees will also provide shade to
OL,16,Fensure that less water evaporates out
OL,17,Fof the ground.
