OL,3,CNew native woodland set to be created
OL,4,Cin Scottish Borders
OL,6,FThe type of trees that are being
OL,7,Fplanted have been carefully chosen to
OL,8,Fmatch local woodland with seed drones
OL,9,Fbeing used on higher locations.
OL,11,FSteve Garbett, Woodland Creation
OL,12,FProject Manager, said: "The
OL,13,Fprojections are with climate change
OL,14,Fthat problems are going to be
OL,15,Fexasperated in the future.
OL,17,F"That ties in with what we are looking
OL,18,Fat already and trees that are planted
OL,19,Ftoday are going to take 20 or 30 years
OL,20,Fto establish.
